pages.text:
Discover the enchanting setting of Lazy Oaks RV Park, where the charm of Florida's gulf coast comes alive under the shelter of ancient Grand Oak trees. Our superb location, between St. Pete and Bradenton, offers unparalleled convenience to an array of attractions.
At Lazy Oaks, water, sewer, and garbage services are all included for your peace of mind. You'll also find on-site laundry facilities.
For leisure activities, the
Terra Ceia Bay Country Club
is just a stone's throw away, welcoming guests to indulge in pool, golf, and pickleball. As for beaches, we're surrounded by the Gulf Coast's finest, including the pristine shores of Coquina Beach, Anna Maria Island, and St. Pete Beach. Plus, don't forget the free island trolley or catch a ride on the water via the
Gulf Islands Ferry
for convenient transportation.
Within a 3-mile radius, you'll find
Ellenton Prime Outlet Mall
, Walmart, CVS, Walgreens, and Publix, catering to your shopping and everyday needs.
And if you're in the mood for adventure, fine arts, museums, kayaking, fishing, and boat charters are all within a few minutes' drive. With Sarasota and St. Pete Airports both within a 30-minute drive, Lazy Oaks RV Park truly offers the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.
